CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776315854
OL,3,CChancellor cuts bills for thousands
OL,4,Cmore firms as she continues Washington
OL,5,Ctalks
OL,7,FDuring her trip, she has stepped up
OL,8,Fcriticism of US-Israeli military
OL,9,Faction in Iran, saying war was a
OL,10,F"mistake" and has not made the world a
OL,11,Fsafer place.
OL,13,FHer comments came as she was due to
OL,14,Fmeet US treasury secretary Scott
OL,15,FBessent, who has referred to the
OL,16,Fimpact of the war as "short-term
OL,17,Fvolatility for long-term gain" which
OL,18,Fhe said would prevent Tehran
OL,19,Fdeveloping a nuclear weapon.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@IO]xD@VOUyD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
