CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776315854
OL,3,CChancellor cuts bills for thousands
OL,4,Cmore firms as she continues Washington
OL,5,Ctalks
OL,7,FMs Reeves also cautioned against knee-
OL,8,Fjerk responses to the cost-of-living
OL,9,Fcrisis triggered by the war in a joint
OL,10,Fstatement with international
OL,11,Fcounterparts at the IMF.
OL,13,FIn a bid to help businesses hit by
OL,14,Frising costs, a plan announced last
OL,15,Fsummer to cut electricity bills by up
OL,16,Fto 25% for more than 7,000 UK
OL,17,Fbusinesses will be expanded to cover
OL,18,F10,000 firms.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776315854
OL,3,CChancellor cuts bills for thousands
OL,4,Cmore firms as she continues Washington
OL,5,Ctalks
OL,7,FThe British Industrial Competitiveness
OL,8,FScheme (BICS) will cut costs by up to
OL,9,F#40 per megawatt-hour from 2027 by
OL,10,Fexempting businesses from certain
OL,11,Fextra charges that currently support
OL,12,Fgreen energy and back-up power supply
OL,13,Fsystems.
OL,15,FAn additional one-off payment in 2027
OL,16,Fwill be given to an extra 3,000
OL,17,Fbusinesses, including companies in the
OL,18,Fautomotive, aerospace, steel and
OL,19,Fpharmaceuticals sectors.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776315854
OL,3,CChancellor cuts bills for thousands
OL,4,Cmore firms as she continues Washington
OL,5,Ctalks
OL,7,FThe Government said it will also cover
OL,8,Fthe support firms would have received
OL,9,Fif the BICS had been in place from
OL,10,Fthis month.
OL,12,FThe scheme is expected to be worth up
OL,13,Fto #600 million per year from next
OL,14,FApril.
OL,16,FMs Reeves said: "This Government has
OL,17,Fthe right plan for the economy:
OL,18,Fbacking British industry, cutting
OL,19,Felectricity costs and building a
OL,20,Fstronger, more resilient future.
OL,26,@xD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776315854
OL,3,CChancellor cuts bills for thousands
OL,4,Cmore firms as she continues Washington
OL,5,Ctalks
OL,7,F"Today's announcement will cut energy
OL,8,Fbills for over 10,000 manufacturers,
OL,9,Fhelping businesses to compete, win and
OL,10,Fcreate good jobs across the country,
OL,11,Fand to deliver our modern industrial
OL,12,Fstrategy."
OL,14,FBusiness Secretary Peter Kyle said:
OL,15,F"We are a Government of action, and
OL,16,Fwhen global instability puts
OL,17,Fbusinesses under pressure we'll always
OL,18,Fdo what's needed to support them and
OL,19,Fensure Britain's resilience.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@JO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776315854
OL,3,CChancellor cuts bills for thousands
OL,4,Cmore firms as she continues Washington
OL,5,Ctalks
OL,7,F"By extending the reach of BICS by
OL,8,F40%, we're acting decisively to tackle
OL,9,Fthe number one issue that businesses
OL,10,Fface head-on."
OL,12,FHousehold energy bills are forecast to
OL,13,Fincrease this year because of the
OL,14,Fconflict pushing up global oil and gas
OL,15,Fprices, while motorists are already
OL,16,Ffeeling the impact of higher costs at
OL,17,Fthe pump.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776315854
OL,3,CChancellor cuts bills for thousands
OL,4,Cmore firms as she continues Washington
OL,5,Ctalks
OL,7,FMs Reeves has signalled that any
OL,8,Fenergy bill help this year will be
OL,9,Ftargeted at the poorest households,
OL,10,Frather than a universal bailout of the
OL,11,Ftype offered by Liz Truss when she was
OL,12,Fprime minister after the Russian
OL,13,Finvasion of Ukraine.
OL,15,FThe White House has said talks are
OL,16,Fongoing about holding fresh face-to-
OL,17,Fface negotiations between the US and
OL,18,FIran and that Washington had not yet
OL,19,Fformally requested an extension of the
OL,20,Fceasefire due to expire next Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/8
